		<title>加拿大央行降息決議後，美元兌加幣小幅走高</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/usdcad-higher-boc-rate-cut</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:36:39 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[市場新聞及觀點]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[USDCAD]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[最近的新聞]]></category>
