										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>加拿大就業和美國製造業數據將主導<a href="https://www.atfx.com.bz/zh-hant/markets/forex-trading" target="_blank" rel="noopener">美元兌加幣</a>週五的交易。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-26613 aligncenter" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/USDCAD-Daily-Chart.png" alt="USDCAD - Daily Chart" width="757" height="591" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/USDCAD-Daily-Chart.png 757w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/USDCAD-Daily-Chart-300x234.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 757px) 100vw, 757px" /></p>
